comments: I happen to think she was very helpful! She was an awesome professor when I had her and you can tell she\'s willing to bend over backwards to help her students. The class was also really interesting. I\'d take it over again if I could.

I really enjoyed her and learned a lot, however her class is more difficult than most. I am fairly confident I got the only A in the class, and even on single tests only one or 2 people got A\'s. She makes strides to help her students where they are struggling though, so I feel if others had put in the effort I did an A wouldn\'t be too difficult.
It\'s your typical lecture class. Minimal interaction with the class and she uses powerpoint presentations. You can easily read your book and pass this class.

she is not very helpful at all all she does is talk talk talk our final there was a review session but for people who worked couldn\'t go during the day and the people in night classes couldn\'t attend because it was being given the same time as class was in session and test were given!
